title: La Tienda Latina
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A casual restaurant where you order and pay at the counter, and food is brought to the table. Has a vegetarian section (please advise HappyCow if there are vegan options!- thanks) on the menu with 8 marked dishes, including lacto vegetarian burrito, quesadilla, and quesadilla de hongos (with fresh grilled vegetables). Good size portion.
